{"tid":433873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【JJ插沙】喉嚨好似比野卡住","createTime":"2017-10-12T18:03:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T19:03:49.000Z","uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"52adb55a62a77958b4ea17a14ae8f812ca4693d9","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:03:16.000Z","msg":"今日食薯片唔小心未咬就吞左一塊碎碎，好似卡住左係喉嚨，當時覺得好似吞左落去，但喉嚨都仲有薯片隻味。之後一直覺得有野卡住，食完飯都仲有異物感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扁桃腺有啲發炎，見到紅紅地，有啲痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 岩岩好辛苦先咳左少少碎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我應該點"},{"pid":"afc71c69f5004431e2988ac7902514131c4b91a4","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:03:47.000Z","msg":"唔睇醫生會唔會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食薯片卡住真係好7呀"},{"pid":"92f76d852ffda05a0b00e686bf581d2d54c8d878","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"救命啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7416aa4e88b73b3f253f8fe4c414f97c97c605e2","tid":433873,"uid":65629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:20:01.000Z","msg":"點解唔睇醫生"},{"pid":"97490bf6ceecc2740869f2ad70882d960d403f29","tid":433873,"uid":114271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:22:11.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦<br />\n我以前未割扁桃腺個陣都成日俾野食啊 魚骨啊 卡住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好彩我老母又勁可以幫我直接扯返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係建議你睇醫生好 發炎可大可小"},{"pid":"9fd2ddd975f59fa75fee2287630a749eba9898be","tid":433873,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:43:58.000Z","msg":"醫生幫你唔到拎出黎<br />\n去急症排啦"},{"pid":"efc3b446c3ff0f2a14ed9f28a7bb07adc96855eb","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇醫生啦<br />\n我以前未割扁桃腺個陣都成日俾野食啊 魚骨啊 卡住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過好彩我老母又勁可以幫我直接扯返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係建議你睇醫生好 發炎可大可小</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好7呀人地食魚卡，我食薯片卡，睇下聽日情況點再去睇下睇唔睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該兩位巴打"},{"pid":"2b48099db1954fc3ba021cd5a3c3779be9ce7332","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:45:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生幫你唔到拎出黎<br />\n去急症排啦</blockquote><br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要照鏡個啲野"},{"pid":"29287859ec5f0a30c2fa3e69d56a34ce931605a1","tid":433873,"uid":137647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:48:33.000Z","msg":"全香港第一個俾薯片「勤」死既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9227f92526fe60f420fec7ce33a5930d5843da65","tid":433873,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T18:55:59.000Z","msg":"你唔係卡住 係界損左"},{"pid":"53e33b268fa2027c3f6fae08d5f7d427f8a5e7a4","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔係卡住 係界損左</blockquote><br />\n但我真係咳左啲碎出黎，個隻薯片唔係平時啲薄薯片，係厚啲硬啲個隻薯片"},{"pid":"8c22b7fb1ee96901a5acb79e8370397cba55f47a","tid":433873,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:02:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫生幫你唔到拎出黎<br />\n去急症排啦</blockquote><br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要照鏡個啲野</blockquote><br />\n唔駛，用夾，但隻夾普通醫生冇<br />\n損就梗，係差舊薯片有冇軟左落肚，冇軟你就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d51ce8ee4b57a6627756ff905429afd06e3c8d2","tid":433873,"uid":63651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T19:03:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醫生幫你唔到拎出黎<br />\n去急症排啦</blockquote><br />\n吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪要照鏡個啲野</blockquote><br />\n唔駛，用夾，但隻夾普通醫生冇<br />\n損就梗，係差舊薯片有冇軟左落肚，冇軟你就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我可唔可以等佢自己林左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}